#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga"
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 27. Saññāsutta → pañcamabhikkhuaparibhāgiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Saññāsutta"
msgstr "27. Non-Decline for Mendicants"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.24"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.27:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that prevent decline."

msgctxt "an7.27:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha … pe …."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention …"

msgctxt "an7.27:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that prevent decline?"

msgctxt "an7.27:1.4"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū aniccasaññaṃ bhāvessanti; vuddhiyeva, "
"bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni."
msgstr "As long as the mendicants develop the perceptions of impermanence …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.27:2.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū anattasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … pe …"
msgstr "not-self …"

msgctxt "an7.27:2.2"
msgid "asubhasaññaṃ bhāvessanti …"
msgstr "ugliness …"

msgctxt "an7.27:2.3"
msgid "ādīnavasaññaṃ bhāvessanti …"
msgstr "drawbacks …"

msgctxt "an7.27:2.4"
msgid "pahānasaññaṃ bhāvessanti …"
msgstr "giving up …"

msgctxt "an7.27:2.5"
msgid "virāgasaññaṃ bhāvessanti …"
msgstr "fading away …"

msgctxt "an7.27:2.6"
msgid "nirodhasaññaṃ bhāvessanti;"
msgstr "cessation,"

#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.27:3.1"
msgid ""
"vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. Yāvakīvañca, "
"bhikkhave, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā bhikkhūsu ṭhassanti, imesu ca "
"sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu, bhikkhū sandississanti; vuddhiyeva, "
"bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"they can expect growth, not decline. As long as these seven principles that "
"prevent decline last among the mendicants, and as long as the mendicants are "
"seen following them, they can expect growth, not decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.27:3.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
